2. Comprehensive Terms Page Prompt

  Here's a complete prompt to create the VexioHQ Terms page that covers everything:

  Create a comprehensive Terms & Conditions page for https://vexiohq.com/terms that covers
  the following for VexioHQ - a B2B/B2C technology company with multiple product verticals
  (Sales, Marketing, HRM, Expense Management, and future products).

  === PAGE STRUCTURE ===

  1. TERMS OF SERVICE
     - Acceptance of terms
     - Eligibility (age 18+, business authorization)
     - Account registration and responsibilities
     - Permitted use and prohibited activities
     - Intellectual property rights
     - Service modifications and termination
     - Limitation of liability
     - Indemnification
     - Governing law (California/Delaware)
     - Dispute resolution

  2. PRIVACY POLICY
     - Information we collect (personal, business, usage data)
     - How we use information
     - Data sharing and third parties
     - Data retention
     - Security measures
     - User rights (access, correction, deletion)
     - Cookies and tracking
     - International data transfers
     - Children's privacy (no under 13)
     - Contact information for privacy concerns

  3. SMS/TEXT MESSAGING TERMS (CRITICAL FOR TWILIO)
     - Consent to receive SMS
     - Types of messages (transactional, promotional, alerts)
     - Message frequency
     - Standard messaging rates apply
     - Opt-out instructions (Reply STOP to unsubscribe)
     - Opt-in confirmation (Reply START/YES to subscribe)
     - Help instructions (Reply HELP for assistance)
     - Supported carriers
     - No guarantee of delivery
     - Contact for SMS questions

  4. EMAIL COMMUNICATION TERMS
     - Consent to receive emails
     - Types of emails (transactional, marketing, updates)
     - Unsubscribe process
     - CAN-SPAM compliance

  5. VOICE/PHONE COMMUNICATION TERMS
     - Consent to receive calls
     - Call recording disclosure
     - AI voice agent disclosure
     - Opt-out of calls

  6. DATA PROCESSING AGREEMENT (for B2B)
     - GDPR compliance
     - Data processor responsibilities
     - Sub-processors
     - Data breach notification

  7. ACCEPTABLE USE POLICY
     - Prohibited content
     - Spam policy
     - Abuse reporting

  8. PRODUCT-SPECIFIC TERMS
     - VexioSales terms
     - Marketing automation terms
     - HRM product terms
     - Expense management terms
     - Future products clause

  9. BILLING & REFUNDS
     - Payment terms
     - Subscription billing
     - Refund policy
     - Cancellation

  10. CONTACT INFORMATION
      - Company: Data Tranquil Inc (DBA VexioHQ)
      - Email: legal@vexiohq.com / support@vexiohq.com
      - Address: [Your business address]
      - Phone: [Support phone]

  === KEY COMPLIANCE REQUIREMENTS ===

  - TCPA (Telephone Consumer Protection Act) - SMS consent
  - CAN-SPAM - Email marketing
  - CCPA (California Consumer Privacy Act)
  - GDPR (if serving EU customers)
  - COPPA (Children's Online Privacy)
  - SOC 2 readiness language

  === SMS SPECIFIC LANGUAGE (REQUIRED BY CARRIERS) ===

  Include exactly:
  "By providing your phone number, you consent to receive SMS messages from VexioHQ
  and its products. Message frequency varies. Message and data rates may apply.
  Reply STOP to unsubscribe. Reply HELP for help. Carriers are not liable for
  delayed or undelivered messages."

  === STYLE ===

  - Professional legal language but readable
  - Clear section headings
  - Last updated date at top
  - Version number
  - Table of contents with anchor links
  - Mobile-friendly formatting

  === COMPANY DETAILS ===

  Company: Data Tranquil Inc
  DBA: VexioHQ
  Type: S-Corp
  Products: VexioSales, VexioMarketing, VexioHRM, VexioExpense, future verticals
  Website: vexiohq.com
  Support Email: support@vexiohq.com
  Legal Email: legal@vexiohq.com